                        <h2 style="color: rgb(255,255,255);margin-top: -140px;font-size: 70px;width: 756px;margin-bottom: -120px;font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;"><br><strong>What is TUSTOS?</strong><br><br></h2>
                        <p style="color: rgb(255,255,255);width: 775px;margin-top: -70px;font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;"><br>TUSTOS is a comprehensive financial tracking website that offers users various tools to manage their finances. It has a Tracker feature that monitors expenses, investments, and savings, as well as a Calculator that computes loans, mortgages, interest, retirement, and tax. TUSTOS also provides a Financial Guide that offers educated financial advice and decisions based on the user's data to improve their overall financial situation. Additionally, it has a Budget Manager that aids in financial decisions by reminding the user of their specific budget and expenses. The Reports feature provides the user with detailed reports of their spending habits, income, and savings, while Notifications keep the user updated on overspending, upcoming bills, and other financial matters. Finally, Bill Tracking allows the user to track their upcoming bills and due dates to avoid late payments. <br><br></p>
